---
title: Charred Zucchini & Bean Quesadillas with Fresh Romaine Salad & Lime Crema
description: Cumin and chili powder give a one-two punch of spice and smokiness to these jam-packed veggie quesadillas. Worry not— tangy lime crema and a refreshingly crisp romaine salad help cool things off.  We think this might be your new go-to quesadilla recipe!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/555612c0fd2cb9641f8b4568.
